Study Schedule

Fill in your class schedule, formulate your own exclusive tasks according to the class schedule, arrange the planning time reasonably, quickly pick up your fragment time, and become a time management master.

Pomodoro Timer

Developing the habit of timing while studying can help increase efficiency.
The use of the Pomodoro clock is to improve the concentration of doing things, so as to achieve a significant effect of doing more with less, try it quickly!

Learning Route

The learning route adopts a five-step learning method, that is, according to the study, most tasks can be divided into five steps, our consistent habit is pre-class preparation, class learning, homework, pre-exam review and exams constitute our learning stage, in essence, whether it is learning or work, we can divide it into five steps to solve problems well, and it is easier to help us assign complex tasks.

Sharing Community

Sharing community is to allow users of the software to share their daily happiness and gains on the community, and make their own daily summary.
Speaking to the community is anonymous, so users can speak freely, and they can also share their daily experiences and learning methods on the community, and I heard that the joy of sharing is double happiness!
